name: Sidewinder Crossbody
description:
Our vintage inspired throwback to the saddle bags of the 60's. 
This hand stitched vegetable tanned leather bag features a large interior pocket, our custom cast solid brass ring, and a raw edge flap. 
It is designed to sit low on the hip. 

Our bags age gracefully and only get better with time.

Approximate dimensions: 
Height: 9"
Width: 11"
Depth: 4"
Strap : 51"

All bags are made to order, please allow 7-10 days for creation.
